@vvysotskyi 
>  Let's set <useSystemClassLoader>false</useSystemClassLoader> for maven-surefire-plugin

Look's like this problem occurs only in Debian OpenJDK build: https://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?bug=911925

I think the tests are failed because the misused of Hook, running TestCaseNullableTypes#testCaseNullableTypesVarchar alone on master gets the error either.
we can put `static {
    Hook.REL_BUILDER_SIMPLIFY.add(Hook.propertyJ(false));
  }` somewhere to keep the old way instead of adding a new one to the Hook, but the final solution is to fix the errors in the tests.
I think it would still get the errors when close the hook after finishing planning.

